  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Holistic Care for 450 HIV Positive Thai Families</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many Thai HIV affected families live in poverty, are marginalized, and their children at risk. Siam-Care supports over 440 families transforming lives and empowering people through a holistic approach. We provide psychosocial support, access to health &amp; welfare, education scholarships (259 children, 2012), family reconciliation,awareness raising &amp; advocacy on HIV &amp; legal rights. Families include widows, grandparents caring for (orphaned) children. Our work reduces HIV/AIDS related social stigma.</narrative>
  </description>
